<section id="rdb_lexicographicResources">
    <title>Database table: <literal>lexicographicResources</literal></title>
    <para>Implements the <olink targetptr="core_lexicographicResource">lexicographicResource</olink>
        object type.</para>

    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Columns</title>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>id: int</literal>, primary key</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>title: nvarchar</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>uri: nvarchar</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>langCode: varchar</literal></para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    
    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Comment</title>
        <listitem>
            <para>If the database is designed to contain only one lexicographic resource then this table,
                including all foreign keys in other tables that reference it, is
                not <glossterm>required</glossterm> to be implemented.</para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    
</section>
